{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 7 shows representative images of M 87 * produced with each of the five imaging methods using data from both calibration pipelines.",
    "Images are shown for all four bands on April 21 and April 25.",
    "For the DIFMAP and RML methods, we present fiducial images.",
    "For THEMIS and Comrade, we display a random sample from the posterior.",
    "We first discuss images from the band 3 data on April 21, which represent (together with band 4) the best (u, v) coverage and the most stable imaging results."
  ]
}